{"tid":1988203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［召喚清算師］有手足提供投訴紅底法官方法","createTime":"2020-04-25T05:04:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T11:40:34.000Z","uid":207967,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"10373c1fa9c2c04c6f103285e96b6cd2bbe4cbc2","tid":1988203,"uid":207967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T05:04:16.000Z","msg":"【投訴郭偉健法官 - 言論偏頗，不應再審理修例案】<br />\n<br />\n一、郭偉健法官判刑理由網上瘋傳，在此不贅。其所作的偏頗言論，已嚴重超出其判刑所需考慮因素，包括考慮與本案毫無關係、且未判決的機場事件等，已影響嚴重影響其判決的公正性，但奈何只有律政司可以上訴。<br />\n<br />\n二、郭偉健法官正處理案件包括(預審未必等同正審*)：<br />\n<br />\n1. 白衣人無差別襲擊市民（7人）暴動罪、有意圖傷人；<br />\n2. 裝修工人6 月圍堵警總部，被控暴動罪；<br />\n3. 44名男女7月28 日出現於示威衝突，被控暴動等罪名；<br />\n4. 中槍中五生與另外6人被起訴暴動縱火和襲警等5項罪名<br />\n<br />\n三、郭偉健法官作出如此言論，實在已不適合再審理任何上述說與反修例運動有關的案件，辯方應提出撤換法官：（<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wclawrencelau/photos/a.605210763167543/1109281646093783/?type=3&amp;theater）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwclawrencelau%2Fphotos%2Fa.605210763167543%2F1109281646093783%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater%EF%BC%89&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKhzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=8b47ef34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wclawrencelau/photos/a.605210763167543/1109281646093783/?type=3&amp;theater）</a><br />\n<br />\n四、一般市民可以做咩？可以向司法機構作出投訴。雖然司法機構不會接納就判決而提出的投訴，但針對法官的政治言論並不是針對其判決，司法機構有權處理。雖然未必有實際作用，但起碼令司法機構知道事件有幾嚴重，唔好再畀改修例案佢處理，起碼唔好畀佢咁易升職先啦。<br />\n<br />\n五、簡單而言，你只需要填左份form，留姓名同聯絡地址，郵寄畀高院，首席區域法院法官高勁修就會處理。2017年都有四宗判定投訴屬實，最後法院領導向該裁判官給予意見。正如前述，係無咩實際作用，但簽白宮聯署都簽左成年，唔差在簽埋呢個？<br />\n<br />\n六、有心人可整份template。<br />\n<br />\n【投訴程序係下面】：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.judiciary.hk/doc/en/about_us/complaintsjjoleaflet.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.judiciary.hk%2Fdoc%2Fen%2Fabout_us%2Fcomplaintsjjoleaflet.pdf&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKhzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=f27aa78d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.judiciary.hk/doc/en/about_us/complaintsjjoleaflet.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n【投訴表格係下面】：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.judiciary.hk/doc/en/about_us/complaintsjjoleaflet.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.judiciary.hk%2Fdoc%2Fen%2Fabout_us%2Fcomplaintsjjoleaflet.pdf&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKhzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=f27aa78d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.judiciary.hk/doc/en/about_us/complaintsjjoleaflet.pdf</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.judiciary.hk/doc/zh/court_services_facilities/complaintsjjo/complaintsjjoform_chi.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.judiciary.hk%2Fdoc%2Fzh%2Fcourt_services_facilities%2Fcomplaintsjjo%2Fcomplaintsjjoform_chi.pdf&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKhzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=44d03827\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.judiciary.hk/doc/zh/court_services_facilities/complaintsjjo/complaintsjjoform_chi.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\nFrom fb: Tze Short Szxeto"},{"pid":"6fc1d46a94ca51fa3db5e5aa63c52e2f4b46c316","tid":1988203,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T05:04:59.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"de04ea6fcc04d02477e943d1dd3892620fcfa780","tid":1988203,"uid":246023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T05:05:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d549ec4d1377de82af3270f7068c648b40f5707","tid":1988203,"uid":218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T05:05:27.000Z","msg":"推爆佢"},{"pid":"81da2faaf7c46b3286e4b80510b19874dde27b2b","tid":1988203,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T05:05:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ea1ee70a9ddf115c036e33fc352170b90ac711","tid":1988203,"uid":207967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T05:06:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"711cecb07c231e30d949d5e8a4d1b7dea818c74a","tid":1988203,"uid":207967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T05:07:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0506dad8c78232ba23a70b50e306e052f8c7811c","tid":1988203,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T05:07:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5a3d384b8fae00393ba54e7ecf7866b9dcae87","tid":1988203,"uid":207967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T05:07:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7225b46b96a40782a6566b51e70293d7d61456de","tid":1988203,"uid":121173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T05:09:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9a766ea9d4ec8ef806c64b11c5482d0b4596b3c","tid":1988203,"uid":146651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T05:11:38.000Z","msg":"推 做左先<br />\n永遠唔到最後唔會知有冇用"},{"pid":"81b1f3bfb9e7775bd94b916f14fa05d7d5375841","tid":1988203,"uid":266805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T05:13:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2d21f958ddb0e1626dd228